title: RHOA: Let's Get Together and Feel Alright
description: The Real Housewives of Atlanta head to Jamaica for their cast trip, and love is in the air for Kenya! Sort of. Not really. Meanwhile, Marlo challenges Ralph's parenting choices, which doesn't sit too well with Kandi.
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
